   "source": [
    "# make a plot\n",
    "from pylab import *\n",
    "from matplotlib.patches import Ellipse\n",
    "\n",
    "delta = 45.0 # degrees\n",
    "\n",
    "angles = arange(0, 360+delta, delta)\n",
    "ells = [Ellipse((1, 1), 4, 2, a) for a in angles]\n",
    "\n",
    "a = subplot(111, aspect='equal')\n",
    "\n",
    "for e in ells:\n",
    "    e.set_clip_box(a.bbox)\n",
    "    e.set_alpha(0.1)\n",
    "    a.add_artist(e)\n",
    "\n",
    "xlim(-2, 4)\n",
    "ylim(-1, 3)\n",
    "\n",
    "show()"
   ]
